description:
Comprehensive end-to-end integration test script with detailed logging at every step.
File: __tests__/e2e-integration.test.ts AND scripts/e2e-test.sh

This is NOT a Vitest unit test — it is a scripted end-to-end validation that runs against
a live (or mocked) instance. It can also be adapted as a Vitest integration test with mocked Gemini.

=== SCENARIO 1: Core Creation Loop ===
Purpose: Verify the golden path from spec §13.2 Shot 2

Steps:
1. [LOG] Start E2E test: Core Creation Loop
2. Start dev server (bun run dev)
3. [LOG] Server started on port 3000
4. Open WebSocket connection to backend
5. [LOG] WebSocket connected: {url, readyState}
6. Verify connection status indicator shows "Connected" (green)
7. [LOG] Connection indicator state: {color, text}
8. Simulate audio input OR send text message: "I have been thinking about the launch timeline. The API migration is the biggest risk, and partner readiness will be a problem. The compliance review scares me. And we need documentation before anything ships."
9. [LOG] Message sent at {timestamp}
10. Wait for tool calls (up to 10 seconds)
11. [LOG] Tool calls received: {count, names, timestamps}
12. For each create_card tool call:
    a. [LOG] Tool call: create_card | args: {title, body, tags, status, placement}
    b. Verify: tool response includes artifact_id, status: "created", position
    c. [LOG] Tool response: {artifact_id, status, position}
    d. Verify: WebSocket notification sent to frontend with ghost flag
    e. [LOG] Frontend notification: {artifact_id, ghost: true}
    f. Verify: Firestore document exists for this artifact
    g. [LOG] Firestore check: {exists: true, document_data}
13. Verify: at least 3 cards created (spec says 3-5 per thought burst)
14. [LOG] Total cards created: {count}
15. Verify: no audio narration during card creation (agent did not speak)
16. [LOG] Agent audio output during creation: {bytes: 0, silent: true}
17. Wait for user silence period (2+ seconds)
18. Verify: agent speaks brief insight after pause
19. [LOG] Agent spoke after pause: {transcription, timing}
20. [LOG] SCENARIO 1 COMPLETE: {passed: true/false, duration_ms}

=== SCENARIO 2: Ghost Card → Solid Transition ===
